To install the pyqt6 follow the below steps.

1. Download and install the last version of python.
2. Download and install pip (package installer for python), 
   in the terminal you can run code:
        >> python get-pip.py
3. Using pip install the pyqt6 by using the following code:
        >> pip install pyqt6
4. Install the pyqt6 tools to be able to use QtDesigner app.
        >> pip install pyqt6-tools

To use the QtDesigner app go to the qt bin folder and look for designer.exe file.
   
    <<Qt Directory>>\Qt\6.5.2\mingw_64\bin\designer.exe